      <title>That was something special. Thank you to everyone who joined us for Kala’s Kimch...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DWBvFKECBdp/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/653386843_1295348835988242_9215092544076061844_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NTU2OTgxODU5NDMxODE4NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=K990p1_TS3cQ7kNvwGB3Csg&amp;_nc_oc=Adouvd8Q6YgdKyPMP-Rn4EWjIIXmHb841N9Fw8GCmwfxbgMnsHp9pdu_3OPs8Gig6Qk&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=-QcWciF1OHjlnrjpjmkGew&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzwPWmMUXuchZ6H743cY-_ahIDRqfdxN_F-oSheLKTIng&amp;oe=69C910C7" alt="Instagram billede fra @kalaskimchi" /></p><p><strong>@kalaskimchi</strong></p><p>That was something special.<br/>
<br/>
Thank you to everyone who joined us for Kala’s Kimchi Yum Cha at Hongs Special. A full room, shared tables, and plates moving from kitchen to table all day.<br/>
<br/>
To @kalaskimchi , thank you for bringing your flavour into our kitchen. Korean kimchi and Cantonese dim sum on one table, it felt right.<br/>
<br/>
To our team and everyone behind the scenes, thank you for the long hours and steady hands.<br/>
<br/>
And to every guest who showed up, tasted, and trusted us, we’re grateful.<br/>
<br/>
This was more than a pop-up. It was a Copenhagen food collaboration we won’t forget.<br/>
<br/>
📍 Hongs Special, Frederiksberg and Hvidovre<br/>
<br/>
#dimsumcopenhagen #copenhagenfood #popupcopenhagen #cantonesefood #frederiksbergeats</p>]]></description>
